<a href="/akira/dtd/3732-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3732">Blanket declassification&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/6746-4049">farseer2002</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">As a beginning commitment toward openness and transparency - blanket declassify (without review) all federal documents created prior to 1941 in all subject matters.<br/><br/>Nuclear and other sensitive subjects due not exist prior to 1941.</div>
